videos.description: Purdue holds for the last possession of the half and Ryan Cline finishes it with a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cline drills a 3 to end the half

videos.description: Nebraska's Isaiah Roby pushes the ball up the court after stealing it away and then slam home the lob on the other end.
videos.headline: Roby gets the steal and slams home an alley-oop
